<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-25-0422 </DOCNO><TEXT>Competitive pressures are increasing in the electric utility industrydue to a variety of factors. A framework was developed to help utilitiesdeal better with the transition toward increased competition. Variouscompetitive assessment methods, not generally used by electric utilities,are reviewed for their application to an increasingly competitive environment.Four case studies were developed that show the application of competitivemethods by different utilities. 31 figs., 11 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>